{"tid":1098593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=? 元朗木橋頭村工業意外　工人遭貨物夾死","createTime":"2019-04-09T07:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T07:23:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eafe183b039b08ac20af423445c93243cfbdffe6","tid":1098593,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"元朗發生工業意外，跟車工遭貨物夾死。今早(9日)10時12分，公庵路近木橋頭村一貨倉，一名工人駕駛剷車在貨櫃內上貨期間，剷車連貨物夾傷站在旁邊的一名工人，當場重創昏迷，工友見狀大驚報警。<br />\n<br />\n救護員趕至，將姓郭(69歲)男子送往博愛醫院搶救後，證實不治。警方封鎖現場調查，案件列作工業意外跟進，並通知勞工處派員到場。據悉，事發時剷車正準備將一部重型印刷機搬上貨櫃。勞工處發言人表示，接報後已即時派員到現場，正就意外原因展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190409/bkn-20190409103830442-0409_00822_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190409%2Fbkn-20190409103830442-0409_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=be2c833e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190409/bkn-20190409103830442-0409_00822_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"d85dd36e5fdc3fdb171aa07e27110b2fb622d520","tid":1098593,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:22:40.000Z","msg":"政府：$4000派少一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf188680dabc0f49e7ace1027b7bbafa15347cae","tid":1098593,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190409/photo/bkn-20190409103830442-0409_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190409134352\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190409%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190409103830442-0409_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190409134352&h=4ebe7199&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}